rows.label: tlk43200141_04_msg0001
rows.name: Cole-san's not been too healthy lately.

rows.label: tlk43200141_04_msg0002
rows.name:
And I know Ion-chan's been
worrying about it a lot.

rows.label: tlk43200141_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Bajena Playhouse is still running
as usual, for now, anyway.

rows.label: tlk43200141_04_msg0004
rows.name:
But I dunno how they'll keep
it going without Cole-san.

rows.label: tlk43200141_04_msg0005
rows.name:
I might never get my chance
to step out on the stage!
